Package demoreee

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AiPlayer
    The AIPlayer class implements AI mechanisms into the game.
    Character
    The Character class creates the character which the user controls in the game.
    Client
    Client connects to the server and communicates by sending and receiving updates.
    GameMenu
    Main starting class, contains the main UI.
    HumanPlayer
    The HumanPlayer class implements mechanisms such as user inputted controls or the level reset.
    InitContent
    The InitContent class creates in game content such as coins entities and hazards.
    LevelData
    The LevelData class implements the level generation mechanism.
    Main
    Most important class; contains the game logic and calls functions from other classes.
    OppPlayer
    The OppPlayer class draws the in game character animations and implements some game mechanisms.
    Server
    The server that is used by the game to connect the players when they want to play multiplayer.
    Sound
    Class that handles everything that is related to sound and contains all functions that are sound-related.
    Spider
    Moving obstacle that drops from the ceiling onto the player after a short delay.
